WEBVTT

00:01.517 --> 00:03.718
Previously on "Shut Eye"...

00:03.719 --> 00:05.199
I have this bad habit

00:05.200 --> 00:07.882
of fucking up the good
things in my life.

00:07.883 --> 00:09.363
And you've been good to me.

00:09.364 --> 00:14.328
So, of course,
I'm going to try to fuck it up.

00:14.329 --> 00:16.490
Police! Get on the ground!

00:16.491 --> 00:18.013
It's okay, Charlie.

00:20.776 --> 00:24.859
Linda would say that
you're feeding my delusion.

00:24.860 --> 00:27.061
I'm feeding your curiosity,

00:27.062 --> 00:29.624
which is something you cannot
have enough of in this business.

00:29.625 --> 00:33.387
Fonso Marks of the Gypsies.

00:33.388 --> 00:35.978
And you fuck with Gypsies,

00:37.352 --> 00:39.398
Gypsies fuck you.

00:40.716 --> 00:42.116
All right.

00:42.117 --> 00:44.559
I asked a question, I got an answer.

00:44.560 --> 00:46.200
No hard feelings, right?

00:46.201 --> 00:48.563
We are on the precipice
of something here.

00:48.564 --> 00:50.685
I know you can feel that.

00:50.686 --> 00:53.078
You don't think I have someone?

00:54.089 --> 00:56.571
It's fucking hard, but I bury it.

00:56.572 --> 00:58.452
I put it to one side
for the sake of the work,

00:58.453 --> 01:01.255
for the sake of what
we are trying to achieve.

01:01.256 --> 01:04.218
Go home to your family, Charlie.

01:04.218 --> 01:05.620
I got a feeling, Foster,

01:05.621 --> 01:07.862
that you and I are going
to be great friends.

01:07.863 --> 01:11.305
There are a lot of rules
involved in being my friend.

01:11.306 --> 01:14.228
And it usually requires
making a few new enemies.

01:14.229 --> 01:15.750
The most important part of the con

01:15.751 --> 01:19.113
is actually identifying the right mark,
right,

01:19.114 --> 01:21.064
someone ready to be taken.

01:21.837 --> 01:24.799
Charlie, please, take over the retreat.

01:24.800 --> 01:27.321
They need help as much as I do.

01:27.322 --> 01:28.963
I can't.

01:28.964 --> 01:30.484
Maggie will be there.

01:30.485 --> 01:32.534
She'll talk you through it.

01:33.889 --> 01:35.770
Let's get you checked out.

01:35.771 --> 01:37.652
I think that's a good idea.

